ed="T" n="0735a26"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0735a26"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000042147"><placeName>京師</placeName><placeName>安國寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A000540">良賁</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0735a27"/><persName key="A000540">釋良賁</persName><ptr target="#n3269"/>，姓<name>郭</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000005190"><placeName>河中</placeName><placeName>虞鄉</placeName></placeName>人也。世襲冠裳，<lb
ed="T" n="0735a28"/>法門之流，不標祖禰<ptr type="glossary" target="#g753"/>，故闕如也。<persName key="A000540">賁</persName>識鑒淵曠，<lb
ed="T" n="0735a29"/>風表<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g713"/>峻越，外通墳典<ptr type="glossary" target="#g418"/>，內善經論，義解<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g544"/>之性，<pb ed="T" n="0735b" xml:id="T50.2061.0735b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0735b01"/>人罕加焉。<date notBefore-iso="+0765-01-30" key="j20005002001190" notAfter-iso="+0766-12-21"><name>永泰</name>中</date>，<persName key="A000095">不空</persName>盛行傳譯，實難其<lb
ed="T" n="0735b02"/>人，<persName key="A000540">賁</persName>預其翻度<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g109"/>。<persName key="A004379">代宗</persName>請為菩薩戒師。因新<lb
ed="T" n="0735b03"/>出《仁王護國經》<ptr target="#n3270"/>，勅令撰疏解判<ptr target="#n3271"/>，曲盡經意，<lb
ed="T" n="0735b04"/>以所住寺為疏目，曰《青龍》也。原夫是經已<lb
ed="T" n="0735b05"/>當三譯，一<date from-iso="+0267-02-11" key="j18186211818975" to-iso="+0268-01-31"><name>晉</name><name>太始</name>三年</date><persName key="A000749">法護</persName>譯一卷，名《仁<lb
ed="T" n="0735b06"/>王般若》；次<placeName key="PL000000048176">秦</placeName><persName key="A001583">羅什</persName>出，名《仁王護國般若波羅<lb
ed="T" n="0735b07"/>蜜》<ptr target="#n3272"/>；次<date from-iso="+0554-02-20" key="j19234551923808" to-iso="+0555-02-08"><name>梁</name><name>承聖</name>三年</date><persName key="A000962">真諦</persName>於<placeName key="PL000000018598"><placeName>洪州</placeName><placeName>寶因寺</placeName></placeName>譯，<lb
ed="T" n="0735b08"/>名《仁王般若》，并疏六卷。然則<name>晉</name>本初翻，方言<lb
ed="T" n="0735b09"/>尚隔。<name>梁</name>朝所譯，隱而不行。偽<name>秦</name>之經，傳流<lb
ed="T" n="0735b10"/>宇內。奈何止言「波羅蜜」而闕「多」字<ptr target="#n755"/>！則是虧<lb
ed="T" n="0735b11"/>其到義。是以<persName key="A004378">肅宗皇帝</persName>齋心沐德，請<persName key="A000095">不空</persName>重<lb
ed="T" n="0735b12"/>譯。及<persName key="A004378">肅皇</persName>晏駕<ptr type="glossary" target="#g756"/>，<persName key="A004379">代宗</persName>成<ref type="person" target="#A004378">先聖</ref>之願言，詔興<lb
ed="T" n="0735b13"/>譯務，勅軍容使<persName key="A009402">魚朝恩</persName>監護<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g55"/>於<placeName key="PL000000042365">南桃園</placeName>，起<lb
ed="T" n="0735b14"/>乎告朔，終乎望日，<ref type="person" target="#A004379">帝</ref>御<placeName key="PL000000042366">承明殿灌頂道場</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0735b15"/>躬執舊經，對譯新本，而復為序，冠于經首<ptr target="#n757"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0735b16"/>仍勅<persName key="A000540">賁</persName>造疏通經。<persName key="A000540">賁</persName>上表曰：「學孤<ptr type="glossary" target="#g758"/>先哲，有<lb
ed="T" n="0735b17"/>玷清流，叨接翻傳，謬膺筆受<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g53"/>。幸揚天闕，<lb
ed="T" n="0735b18"/>親奉德音，令於<placeName key="PL000000042365"><placeName>大明宮</placeName><placeName>南桃園</placeName></placeName>修疏贊演，<lb
ed="T" n="0735b19"/>宸光曲照，不容避席。窮玄珠於貝葉，但益<lb
ed="T" n="0735b20"/>慚惶；捧白璧於丹墀<ptr type="glossary" target="#g751"/>，寧勝報斆<ptr type="glossary" target="#g759"/>。仰酬皇澤，<lb
ed="T" n="0735b21"/>俯課忠勤，既竭愚誠，庶昭玄造。<ptr target="#n760"/>」<persName key="A000540">賁</persName>勤勤筆<lb
ed="T" n="0735b22"/>削，三卷克成<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g761"/>，奏乞流行。復上牋疏：「<date when-iso="+0766-03-30" key="j20009242000924">今年二<lb
ed="T" n="0735b23"/>月<choice resp="sgsz"><sic>二十一</sic><corr>十一</corr></choice>日</date><ptr target="#n3273"/>恩命令在<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042365">內園</ref>修撰經疏，<ref type="person" target="#A000540">微<lb
ed="T" n="0735b24"/>僧</ref>寡學，懼不稱旨。洗心滌慮，扣寂求音，發<lb
ed="T" n="0735b25"/>明起自於天言，加被仰憑於佛力，咸約經<lb
ed="T" n="0735b26"/>論，演暢真宗，亦猶集群玉於<placeName key="PL000000047443">崑山</placeName>，納大川<lb
ed="T" n="0735b27"/>於溟海。火生於木，與兩曜而俱明；識<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g762"/>轉於<lb
ed="T" n="0735b28"/>如<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g763"/>，體一相而等照。成道者，法也；載法者，經<lb
ed="T" n="0735b29"/>也；釋經者，疏也。廣度群有，同於大通，是菩<pb ed="T" n="0735c" xml:id="T50.2061.0735c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0735c01"/>提心，如<ref type="person" target="#A004379">陛下</ref>意。所撰經疏，繕寫畢功，文過<lb
ed="T" n="0735c02"/>萬言，部有三卷。施行竊慚於愚見，裁成冀<lb
ed="T" n="0735c03"/>答於聖恩。并《念誦儀軌》一卷，《承明殿講密嚴<lb
ed="T" n="0735c04"/>經對御記》一卷同進上。輕塵玄覽<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g765"/>，祇畏<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g766"/>無<lb
ed="T" n="0735c05"/>任<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g767"/>。」答詔云：「<ref type="person" target="#A000540">法師</ref>智炬高明，辭峯逈秀，親憑<lb
ed="T" n="0735c06"/><name>梵</name>夾，宣闡微言，幽賾<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g331"/>真宗，演成章疏。開<persName key="A002799">如<lb
ed="T" n="0735c07"/>來</persName>之祕藏，示群有之迷津，貫玉聯珠，鉤深<lb
ed="T" n="0735c08"/>致遠。再三披閱，頗謂精詳。傳之招提<ptr target="#n177"/>，永為<lb
ed="T" n="0735c09"/>法寶也。<ptr target="#n764"/>」皇命褒揚，<name>釋</name>門翕<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g768"/>盛。又屬<placeName key="PL000000042180">章信寺</placeName>初<lb
ed="T" n="0735c10"/>成，<anchor xml:id="beg0735sgsz1"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>報</sic><corr>執</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0735sgsz1"/>疏<anchor xml:id="beg0735sgsz2"/>服膺<anchor xml:id="end0735sgsz2"/>者常數百眾，雖紙貴如玉，無<lb
ed="T" n="0735c11"/>以加焉。其在<placeName key="PL000000042147">安國寺</placeName>講筵，官供不匱。數年<lb
ed="T" n="0735c12"/>之內，歸學如林。<date from-iso="+0772-02-13" key="j20030702003098" to-iso="+0772-03-12"><name>大<anchor xml:id="beg0735002"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>歷</sic><corr>曆</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0735002"/></name>七年正月</date>，<persName key="A000095">不空</persName>奏請<lb
ed="T" n="0735c13"/>入《目錄》，勅依。<persName key="A000540">賁</persName>於<date from-iso="+0771-01-25" key="j20026862003069" to-iso="+0772-02-12">六年</date>徙居<placeName key="PL000000037201">集州</placeName>，教授<lb
ed="T" n="0735c14"/>傳經，不遑<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g769"/>寧處。至<date key="j20049692004969" when-iso="+0777-04-26">十二年三月十日</date>，無疾<lb
ed="T" n="0735c15"/>枕肱，終于<placeName key="PL000000037186">符陽</placeName>，春秋六十一，夏臘二十九。<lb
ed="T" n="0735c16"/><placeName key="PL000000036448">宕渠</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000035703">嘉川</placeName>之人，哀悼法梁摧折，闍維收灰中<lb
ed="T" n="0735c17"/>舍利百餘粒。遺表中進《念誦儀》、《對御記》二卷，<lb
ed="T" n="0735c18"/>以其先進者遂留在內中之故<ptr target="#n3276"/>，令門弟子<lb
ed="T" n="0735c19"/>齎之重進。後於<placeName key="PL000000042189">上都</placeName>城東置墳塔焉，即<date from-iso="+0778-02-06" key="j20052552005608" to-iso="+0779-01-25"><name>大<lb
ed="T" n="0735c20"/>曆</name>十三年</date>也。<persName key="A000540">賁</persName>累朝供奉應制，辭辯富贍，學<lb
ed="T" n="0735c21"/>問高深。末塗淪躓<ptr type="glossary" target="#g770"/>，同<persName key="A011214">利涉</persName>之<anchor xml:id="beg0735sgsz3"/>徙<anchor xml:id="end0735sgsz3"/>移<ptr target="#n858"/>，若<persName key="A005612">神會</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0735c22"/>之流外<ptr target="#n771"/>，吁哉！</p>
